para.para.body:
I conclude that 
                        \Vect{x} = \Vect{0}
                     .

Correct! – Given that 
                        \Vect{y}\neq \Vect{0}
                     , 
                        \proj_{L}(\Vect{x})=\Vect{0}
                      exactly when 
                        \Vect{x} \bullet \Vect{y} = 0
                     . This happens exactly when 
                        \Vect{x}
                      is perpendicular to 
                        \Vect{y}
                     .
